{
  "texts": [
    "Tables and graphs will not be legible in a small popup window, and even lengthier text may be difficult to read.",
    "Therefore, the copilot should ideally have its own dedicated panel in the UI, where intermediate results can optionally be displayed separately for more technical users interested in understanding and modifying the chain of thoughts of the LLM and other specialized agents.",
    "Each of the functionalities highlighted in this paper are critical to the deployment of a marketing analytics copilot.",
    "While not exhaustive, this work highlights a couple of key points about developing a marketing analytics assistant.",
    "First, it is useful to have specialized programs, often called agents, employing different LLMs to perform different tasks."
  ]
}